{"tid":1167626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019 Uniqlo Pokemon UT設計冠軍沒了 中國設計師違反比賽規則遭取消資格","createTime":"2019-05-23T07:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T09:09:33.000Z","uid":12599,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb421f92edffc8a163baafe7dd48d69a295bce3f","tid":1167626,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://driver.cool3c.com/files/3/c4667986-41b9-4fbd-9c80-ebb37992e8d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdriver.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2F3%2Fc4667986-41b9-4fbd-9c80-ebb37992e8d3.jpg&h=b635c98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年Uniqlo與Pokemon都會舉辦UT設計大賽，2019年的「UT GRAND PRIX 2019」取得冠軍的中國籍設計師Li Wen Pei，作品海洋之王遭舉報違反比賽規則。該投稿作品數年前曾販售相關周邊，比賽規章中規定，作品需為首次發表的原創作品，取得冠軍的作品顯然違反規則。目前國外的Uniqlo公告取消該設計師的資格，並將冠軍從缺處理外，未來也不會販售該商品，但目前台灣Uniqlo仍未將得獎作品下架。除冠軍外，另外也有入選作品因違反規定而取消資格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://driver.cool3c.com/files/3/c4667986-41b9-4fbd-9c80-ebb37992e8d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdriver.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2F3%2Fc4667986-41b9-4fbd-9c80-ebb37992e8d3.jpg&h=b635c98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲取得冠軍的作品為海洋之王，設計師為中國籍Li Wen Pei。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://driver.cool3c.com/files/3/d4229795-0f46-4aa2-81da-4088d3cfcc16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdriver.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2F3%2Fd4229795-0f46-4aa2-81da-4088d3cfcc16.jpg&h=3dfc8231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美國Uniqlo已經將冠軍作品下架，並貼出公告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/144041?fbclid=IwAR2faB_V09hCQmV2vfjiMuC9DBDnZ3HqY-oRSsaacjYtvP2OroWIpU5c-5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F144041%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2faB_V09hCQmV2vfjiMuC9DBDnZ3HqY-oRSsaacjYtvP2OroWIpU5c-5w&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=ac696e5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/144041?fbclid=IwAR2faB_V09hCQmV2vfjiMuC9DBDnZ3HqY-oRSsaacjYtvP2OroWIpU5c-5w</a>"},{"pid":"08686c59a3dd8c640f3264e655a80e86864903a2","tid":1167626,"uid":138713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b049cd26d6d5a637140057834fa31c8e682b6b","tid":1167626,"uid":18477,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">該投稿作品數年前曾販售相關周邊</span><br />\n<br />\n即係任記告得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edad15c94fdb331c3aa0e477ed89c275309e88a","tid":1167626,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"支那人真係做乜都柒過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f34eec05a3ba75e2cdecc11e19c960c1e10a4f","tid":1167626,"uid":220458,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"老實講我覺得幾靚"},{"pid":"29a991193e5297d2639c79744408a7066012935f","tid":1167626,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"亞軍咩黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1fd89e1b8fae26f5af6dd0f05c267798880039","tid":1167626,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"講咁多廢話原來係抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}